text: Desiree Carole Heslop (born 28 November 1961), best known as Princess, is a British soul singer who found chart success in the mid-1980s. In the early 1980s, she worked with the afro soul group Osibisa. She is best known for her hit single "Say I'm Your Number One" which made the UK Top Ten in 1985. ==See also== *Sinitta *Sonia *Hazell Dean *Mandy Smith *Mel and Kim *Kylie Minogue *Bananarama *Samantha Fox *Rick Astley *Jason Donovan *Stock Aitken & Waterman Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:British singers
